Global Isopropyl Alcohol Market Insights
Isopropyl Alcohol Market size was valued at USD 5.7 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 8.3 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 4.8% from 2024 to 2030.

Isopropyl Alcohol Market Overview
The Isopropyl Alcohol (IPA) market has witnessed significant growth due to its increasing demand across various industries such as pharmaceuticals, cosmetics, automotive, and chemicals. In 2023, the global IPA market size was valued at approximately USD 6.2 billion and is expected to grow at a CAGR of 4.5% during the forecast period from 2024 to 2031. The expanding use of IPA in sanitizers, cleaning agents, and disinfectants has further driven its demand, especially during and post the COVID-19 pandemic. Moreover, the rising applications of IPA in the electronics and automotive industries for cleaning and degreasing purposes are propelling market growth.

